<br>
I'd like you all to read the first few paragraphs of<br>
my new novel. It's kind of like Lord of the Rings,<br>
serious fantasy medieval stuff, from the perspective<br>
of a Half-Elf girl named Ytra who's just turned 13. <br>
<br>
I have some questions I'd like y'all to answer when<br>
you finish. That's right--YOU get to participate in<br>
deciding Ytra's fate! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
1. What class should Ytra get when she sees the Priests and why?<br>
2. What's your first impression of Ytra and her kin?<br>
3. Should Ytra be the gold thief, or her sister Aiya?<br>
4. What would you like to see Ytra do next?<br>
5. What members of Ytra's family interest you most?<br>
